name: EECS 2020-InfoSec, & CyberSecurity
content: International Conference on Electrical Engineering and Computer Sciences (EECS 2020) will take place from February 18-20 in Guam. This year, we will focus on the theme of “InfoSec, & CyberSecurity”. We sincerely invite submission of abstracts/full papers relevant to “Electrical Engineering and Computer Sciences". Topics are listed but are not restricted to the followings: -InfoSec, & CyberSecurity (Conference Theme) -Biomedical Electronics and Bioinformatics -Communication Engineering -Computer Science Applications -Electronics & Electrical Engineering -Information Engineering -Nano-Electro-Mechanical System -Networking, Communication and Multimedia -Photonics and Optoelectronics -Wireless/Mobile Communication & Computing Submit the paper to http://www.iceecs.org/ Email: eecs@iceecs.org
